{
  "stem": "27347.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My grandmother used to say, he worries more about everybody else than about us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had-- my father educated me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not go to a formal Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in Vienna, every night, I was sitting with a book, the Bible, or-- and translated to me word by word because my father knew a lot.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He remembered-- he could quote everything from the Bible and know what it meant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's the Ashkenazi style of prayer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- once a week he had a mission.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember once sitting in the room very forlorn and lonely and thinking about Vienna and my grandmother, who I missed so terribly.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he came over and he said, do you know what?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would like to take you on a little walk, for a walk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mom, may I go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said, sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he took me on a tour where he came in to a man-- I just give you an example of one house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The maid opened the door, greeted my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the man was very cordial and polite.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was happy to see my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was introduced.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Monies were exchanged.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He gave my grandfather money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My grandfather wrote it down on a list.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He didn't say thank you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I have noticed all this because that was my job now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had nothing else to do but learn and observe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we went to several places and the same thing happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was a little bit intimidated and uncomfortable with this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when we left, my grandfather gave me a lesson.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, when you say thank you, you take the good deed away from that person.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
